transcript:
Aap jis vyakti se baat
Hello?
Hello?
Hanji sir, namaskar.
Namaskar sir, boliye. Sudhanshu baat kar raha hu, IndiaMART se.
Han sir boliye.
Actually maine na ticket open kiya tha, toh mere paas mail revert aaya hai ki thana aur thane ek hi hota hai.
Ek hi nahi hai na sir, alag alag hai.
Maine bola but unhone bola ki pehle alag tha, matlab thane ka thane ka hi naam thana tha, usko change karke thane kar diya gaya hai.
Nahi nahi, woh Mumbai wale baat kar rahe hai na?
Han.
Han haan. Toh hamare idhar ek thana hai, aapke idhar Mumbai mein thane hai.
Uh aur aapka jo thana hai woh kiske nearest mein hai?
Yeh hai na, dekhiye Nagpur hai Nagpur.
Hmm. Nagpur se 40 kilometer dur aata hai.
Ek minute.
Iska district kya padta hai?
Bhandara.
Maharashtra mein hi hai.
Han.
But sir unhone bola ki ek hi hai dono, isliye hum log change nahi kar sakte hai isko.
Nahi na sir, aap ek kaam kariye na, unko mere ko phone karne boliye. Main unse baat kar leta hu woh bhi hai woh.
Hai ki nahi? Theek hai. Theek hai, okay.
Han.
